title: GarminMobileXT_Europe_Nokia_N95_N95-8gb_6110_N82
description:
Full GarminMobileXT 
for use with Nokia N95, N95 8gb, 6110 Navigator or N82
Incl. Western Europe Maps 

Works fine with internal GPS and all files for the programm to work are incl. 
like Keygens, Maps, and so on...

All you need is one of the phones described or another nokia running s60 with internal gps or bluetooth gps... and Win-RAR... 

Have fun Navigating^^
